{"tid":2049923,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE 中文十二篇筆記同解說！第一集：荀子《勸學》","createTime":"2020-06-03T19:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T14:58:16.000Z","uid":264783,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ccbb60e35bc2df54d4da84f871c58731cb09be67","tid":2049923,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:30:55.000Z","msg":"呢排多咗時間 咁就整合返啲DSE12篇Notes 俾返啲補習學生用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然我咁啱首先整合左《勸學》，咁我嘅12篇解說第一炮就奉勸各位中四中五中六嘅DSE考生<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>快啲學習啦</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會將筆記嘅Lihkg放上網，同學應首先透過Lihkg或者YouTube下載，再收聽Youtube 上面嘅課程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n筆記嘅內容係綜合左坊間補習社、補習筆記、書本筆記、出版社筆記等等用多年心血合成嘅傻蠢狗汪汪筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年我都係靠佢喺閱讀度攞5**咋 依家就讀緊港大中文 大家請放心食用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然筆記入面可能會有打錯字、打漏咗少少字嘅情況 方便嘅話同我講返 如果中文閱讀有啲乜嘢疑問都可以喺度提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> DSE加油！！！！<br />\n<br />\n筆記link: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tU6Gl1W5Nu3xQMnhiMhebNsPN2Cg77XZ/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1tU6Gl1W5Nu3xQMnhiMhebNsPN2Cg77XZ%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=47b40104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tU6Gl1W5Nu3xQMnhiMhebNsPN2Cg77XZ/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube link: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/FobYRPzFIW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFobYRPzFIW4&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=1993becd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FobYRPzFIW4</a><br />\n<br />\n建議首先print左份notes出嚟，跟住一路聽一路抄notes。因為坊間嘅筆記只會越來越多，你哋應該下載咗份notes之後，自己抄寫或者更新返老師提醒你哋嘅重點，記得你哋只會越背越多 哈哈哈密瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>記得 Comment, Like 同Subscribe！！如果唔係就冇第二集㗎啦！！ 嬲嬲豬㗎啦！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nDSE諗起都辛苦 不過天道酬勤嘅 中四嗰啲學生要有危機感啦 中五中六嗰啲準備日日訓喺圖書館自修室啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識嘅唔好起我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfc3d2928a3c32a959f5bb93824e0410f592ca0","tid":2049923,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:31:44.000Z","msg":"自推1 用電腦睇可能會好啲 清晰啲"},{"pid":"0448a6565b7e0dea9470f84ad1f490cf47a4b1ce","tid":2049923,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:32:29.000Z","msg":"2 同你地喺出面補習社嘅1小時精讀都幾異曲同工㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78582680e1077383fba3dba2ac05d4a5948b09ce","tid":2049923,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:32:45.000Z","msg":"推3 有啲眼瞓"},{"pid":"3868e68ee6296c1ab995f27afa5066eec834e446","tid":2049923,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"推4 你哋覺得有冇用都要話返俾我聽啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd338624e606ad9792e3a3e727421ae32f375fbe","tid":2049923,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:33:27.000Z","msg":"推5 整咗好多個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120d52b6310d0ac0